<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="caution-vt">caution <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kɔːʃn/    美 /'kɔːʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vt-vi">1.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi 警告；告诫；提醒：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A friend <strong>cautioned</strong> her <strong>against</strong> / <strong>about</strong> taking risks.
朋友警告她不要冒险。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>cautioned</strong> Tom not <strong>to</strong> drive too fast.
她提醒汤姆开车不要太快。</p></div></div>